          <section>
<!-- Begin Post -->
<p>Hey everyone! Rails versions 5.2.5, 6.0.3.6 and 6.1.3.1 have been released. These versions upgrade
Active Storage‚Äôs <a href="https://github.com/rails/marcel">Marcel</a> dependency to version 1.0.0.</p>

<p>Before 1.0.0, Marcel‚Äîwhich is distributed under the terms of the MIT License, like Rails‚Äîindirectly
depended on MIME type data released under the incompatible GNU General Public License. Marcel 1.0.0
instead directly packages MIME type data adapted from <a href="https://tika.apache.org">Apache Tika</a>,
released under the permissive and compatible Apache License 2.0.</p>

<p>Here are the gem checksums:</p>

