          </header>
          <section>
<!-- Begin Post -->
<p>Hey everyone! Rails version 5.2.4.5, 6.0.3.5 and 6.1.2.1 have been released! Those version are
security releases and addresses two issues:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://discuss.rubyonrails.org/t/cve-2021-22880-possible-dos-vulnerability-in-active-record-postgresql-adapter/77129">[CVE-2021-22880] Possible DoS Vulnerability in Active Record PostgreSQL adapter</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://discuss.rubyonrails.org/t/cve-2021-22881-possible-open-redirect-in-host-authorization-middleware/77130">[CVE-2021-22881] Possible Open Redirect in Host Authorization Middleware</a></li>
</ul>

