<!-- Begin Post -->
<p>Hey everyone!  Rails version 6.0.3.4 has been released!  This version is a
security release and addresses one possible XSS attack vector in Actionable
Exceptions.</p>

<p>You can read more about the issue <a href="https://discuss.rubyonrails.org/t/cve-2020-8264-possible-xss-vulnerability-in-action-pack-in-development-mode/76368">here</a>.</p>

