<!-- Begin Post -->
<p>Hi everyone!</p>

<p>Rails 6.0.3.2 has been released!  This version of Rails contains an important
security patch, and you should upgrade!  The release contains only one patch
that addresses CVE-2020-8185.  You can read about CVE-2020-8185 <a href="https://groups.google.com/d/topic/rubyonrails-security/pAe9EV8gbM0">here</a>.</p>

