            <h2>
              <a href="/2017/6/13/Rails-4-2-9-rc1-has-been-released/" rel="bookmark">Rails 4.2.9.rc1 has been released!</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="entry-meta">
              Posted by <span class="vcard"><span class="fn">rafaelfranca</span></span>,
              <span class="published" title="2017-06-13 18:57:28 +0000">June 13, 2017 @  6:57 pm</span>
              
                <span class="categories">in
              
              
                  <a href="/releases/" rel="category tag">Releases</a>
              
              
                </span>
              
            </p>
          </header>
          <section>
<!-- Begin Post -->
<p>Hi everyone,</p>

<p>I am happy to announce that Rails 4.2.9.rc1 has been released.</p>

<p>This is going to be the last bug fix release of the 4.2 series, so please test this release candidate.</p>

<p>If no regressions are found, expect the final release on Monday, June 19, 2017.
If you find one, please open an <a href="https://github.com/rails/rails/issues/new">issue on GitHub</a>
and mention me (@rafaelfranca) on it, so that we can fix it before the final release.</p>

<h2 id="changes-since-428">CHANGES since 4.2.8</h2>

<p>To view the changes for each gem, please read the changelogs on GitHub:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/rails/rails/blob/v4.2.9.rc1/actionmailer/CHANGELOG.md">Action Mailer CHANGELOG</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/rails/rails/blob/v4.2.9.rc1/actionpack/CHANGELOG.md">Action Pack CHANGELOG</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/rails/rails/blob/v4.2.9.rc1/actionview/CHANGELOG.md">Action View CHANGELOG</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/rails/rails/blob/v4.2.9.rc1/activejob/CHANGELOG.md">Active Job CHANGELOG</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/rails/rails/blob/v4.2.9.rc1/activemodel/CHANGELOG.md">Active Model CHANGELOG</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/rails/rails/blob/v4.2.9.rc1/activerecord/CHANGELOG.md">Active Record CHANGELOG</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/rails/rails/blob/v4.2.9.rc1/activesupport/CHANGELOG.md">Active Support CHANGELOG</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/rails/rails/blob/v4.2.9.rc1/railties/CHANGELOG.md">Railties CHANGELOG</a></li>
</ul>

<p><em>Full listing</em></p>

<p>To see the full list of changes, <a href="https://github.com/rails/rails/compare/v4.2.8...v4.2.9.rc1">check out all the commits on
GitHub</a>.</p>

<h2 id="sha-256">SHA-256</h2>

<p>If you‚Äôd like to verify that your gem is the same as the one I‚Äôve uploaded,
please use these SHA-256 hashes.</p>

<p>Here are the checksums for 4.2.9.rc1:</p>

