          <header>
            <h2>
              <a href="/2015/11/6/Rails-4-2-5-rc2-and-4-1-14-rc2-have-been-released/" rel="bookmark">[ANN] Rails 4.2.5.rc2 and 4.1.14.rc2 have been released!</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="entry-meta">
