<p>Hi everyone,</p>

<p>I am happy to announce that Rails 4.2.3.rc1 and 4.1.12.rc1 have been released.</p>

<p>If no regressions are found expect the final release this Thursday, on June 25, 2015.
If you find one, please open an <a href="https://github.com/rails/rails/issues/new">issue on GitHub</a>
and mention me (@rafaelfranca) on it, so that we can fix it before the final release.</p>

