1640674035171d0eb36ff91da9ea8d86f2137261  railties-4.1.11.gem
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Here are the checksums for Rails 4.2.2:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>$ shasum *4.2.2*
a093bdd43d732416f02b1cc39edc4f839b27cc69  actionmailer-4.2.2.gem
