<p>Hi everyone,</p>

<p>I am happy to announce that Rails 4.2.1.rc4 and 4.1.10.rc4 have been released.</p>

<p>There were found some regressions in the last release candidates so, following release process we are
releasing new release candidates.</p>

<p>If no regressions are found expect the final release this Tuesday, on March 17, 2015.
If you find one, please open an <a href="https://github.com/rails/rails/issues/new">issue on GitHub</a>
and mention me (@rafaelfranca) on it, so that we can fix it before the final release.</p>

