<p>Hi everyone,</p>

<p>Rails 4.1.2 and Rails 4.0.6 are finally out. Rails 4.1.2 is the first bug fix release for
the 4.1 series. Rails 4.0.6 includes a lot of bug fixes to make the upgrade path
from Rails 3 easier.</p>

