              <a href="/2014/2/18/Rails_3_2_17_4_0_3_and_4_1_0_beta2_have_been_released/" rel="bookmark">Rails 3.2.17, 4.0.3 and 4.1.0.beta2 have been released!</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="entry-meta">
              Posted by <span class="vcard"><span class="fn">rafaelfranca</span></span>,
              <span class="published" title="2014-02-18 19:17:03 +0000">February 18, 2014 @  7:17 pm</span>
              
