          </header>
          <section>
<!-- Begin Post -->
<p>Hi everyone!</p>

<p>Rails 3.2.17, 4.0.3 and 4.1.0.beta2 have been released!</p>

<p>These three releases contain important security fixes, so please upgrade as soon
as possible! In order to make upgrading as smooth as possible, we‚Äôve only
included commits directly related to each security issue.</p>

<p>The security fixes in 3.2.17 are:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/rubyonrails-security/tfp6gZCtzr4">CVE-2014-0081</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/rubyonrails-security/LMxO_3_eCuc">CVE-2014-0082</a></li>
</ul>

<p>The security fixes in 4.0.3 are:</p>

