                <span class="categories">in
              
              
                  <a href="/releases/" rel="category tag">Releases</a>
              
              
                </span>
              
            </p>
          </header>
          <section>
<!-- Begin Post -->
<p>We‚Äôve pushed out the third release candidate for 1.0 of Rails. This release most prominently fixes a memory leak with render_component (which affected Typo among others), the scaffolding bug, and a number of other small things. Please do upgrade. If you‚Äôre already running 0.14.1 (RC2), then you don‚Äôt need to change anything in the application.</p>
